ADD #ERCH to ioPAY wallet (ios and android compatible)
You will need to add token manually in order to receive pre-sale purchased tokens. Add token manually XRC20 token #ERCH (ERCH Protocol) by smart contract: io19t0g5xfgvmad7742wsek8s28hglth89verynru
1.1. Download IoTX official wallet — ioPay wallet.

https://iotex.io/iopay
Download android version from Google Play — click here
Download Apple ios version from Apple Store — click here
2. Open wallet , save recovery phrase and find option to Add Token.

3. On top righ corner find ‘+’ and add #ERCH token manually by smart

http://erchprotocol.crypto/
